- No helpers unless reused 3+ times.
- No "remove for now" — delete fully (DB, model, API, UI) or don't touch.
- Don't duplicate server logic on the client. API owns truth; UI renders it.
- Match existing patterns (ideas-view, brand-brain-view) before inventing new ones.
- If unsure, ask — don't add abstractions "for later".